comment: Crowley helping family's from world war 2 has given me 10 extra years to my life

This animatic is based on the headcanon that Crowley was Raphael, Archangel of Healing before he fell. Essentially, Aziraphale doesn't know about it and Crowley is scared to tell him because he doesn't want Aziraphale to be intimidated by/scared of him for being a "higher angel".

Finally, after over a month this animatic is complete. I was planning on finishing it sooner but college got in the way. I hope you guys enjoy!
